title: PINK Silky Powder Puff 4.5 Inch (12cm) in a Pretty Satin Bag
description:
Having a hard time finding a powder puff for the body?
You've just found one!

This soft body puff is large enough to use on your body, this is not a compact size puff. Generously sized at 4.5" in diameter and 1" thick. Plush pink furry puff holds powder well, the satin hand strap helps keep puff in your hand. Best used with Dusting Powder, Body Powder or Fragrant Powders - beautiful and practical for daily pampering! Not suitable for Make-Up Applications.  Sold in a Pretty Satin Bag.

If you order this pink puff and one of our white puffs together, you will notice the fabric is a bit different. Same high quality you've come to expect, but the pink puff is made a little different.

This item is also available at www.buypowderpuffs.com

We hope that you will understand that due to the nature of this personal item we cannot accept returns. 
You will be happy to know that the item you receive from us has never been returned or has been in the possession of someone else.

If you would like to try our puffs we recommend ordering just one in case it isn't what you are looking for.

NOTICE: Because each puff is handmade and handsewn the actual size may vary slightly. Although the mfg. states this puff to be 4.5" you may receive one that is a little smaller or a little bigger.
THIS IS NOT A VELOUR/VELVET STYLE PUFF!

NOTICE:
Some people feel that the puff is not fluffy enough or that it holds powder well.
A brand new puff will not actually fluff up big and full until the fibers are filled with powder. Once the fibers fill with powder, the powder will not "Fall Off" the puff.

Please do not judge the puff until you have used it a few times, then you will see it become fuller and larger than it was when it was brand new!

title: HSI PROFESSIONAL Argan Oil LEAVE IN CONDITIONER flat iron thermal protector leaves hair silky and shiny 4oz BOTTLE

It really seems like your hair is in for a fabulous treat!
